highlights.text: Jin has the most spots on Top Songs Hong Kong. “Don’t Say You Love Me” is the highest at #1.
“Close to You” by Jin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Hong Kong, up 119 spots at #55.
“反對無效” by MC 張天賦 has been on Top Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 1559 days straight.
“GO!” by CORTIS is the highest new entry on Top Songs Hong Kong at #60.
